div.div:
Logic Layer being event driven service orientated architecture with two logical pairs of Kubernetes (AKS) clusters - all other logic layer services expected to be instance orientated either through Azure capabilities or via Node.js based Azure Functions
Aggregation - serves to fetc, index and connect data from internal services/partners (i.e. flights, hotels, vehicles)
Service - serves to fulfill Client App requests
All AKS container pods scale to fit demand, Aggregation will have different scale parameters than Service
